      • categoryBitmask

        public final Long categoryBitmask()
        Bitmask for category of collision filtering. Collision happens if ((category1 & collision2) | (category2 & collision1)) is not zero. If not specified, the category_bitmask should be interpreted as being the same as collide_bitmask.

      • categoryBitmask
